  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Obalon Balloon System - Post-Approval Study is a prospective, observational, and
      multi-center study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The Obalon PAS is a 1-year study that includes 6-month of Obalon Balloon therapy in
      conjunction of a weight loss behavior modification (WLBM) program and 6-month of continued
      WLBM program after balloon removal
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
